create vision_beacon pose 1.40 1.00 0 color black channel 2 port 0 index 0 invisible sonar visible obstacle visible laser radius 0.10 
create vision_beacon pose 1.60 1.00 0 color black channel 3 port 0 index 0 visible obstacle visible laser visible sonar radius 0.10 


create box pose 4.00 4.00 0 color black channel -1 port 0 index 0 visible obstacle visible laser visible sonar size 0.10 0.10 

create box pose 1.00 2.00 0 color black channel -1 port 0 index 0 visible obstacle visible laser visible sonar size 0.40 0.40 


